2.19: naaiq teij winb wavq yem Bua Zwrtq mivb mq paag ninb Bua maiq za'kevb penj Bua Eei myenb. sij kxvq ninb Bua za'kevb Bua Eei myenb, ninb Bua Zxg Zauj Bua yem. mq paag ninb Bua Zwrtq mivb zyrug pun Ziv ninb Bua maiq maaib yetg taub zeid Bua Eei myenb.
2.17: paamb ken Zauj yem paamb ken yua'g myenb Eei ka'naaiq Jiaj Jyenq mivb a'q. mq paag haiq taub ei Jyenq Tinb huvb Eei eij zruj, uaq taub zyrug tu'q yetg liud zyavb Jyenq.
2.27: mq paag ki-tug Zeij sivj livb pun meib Bua. sivj livb yaag yem Jyenq meib Bua Eei Hruq, meib Bua zyrug maiq Qyemj zu'g haiq taub Faauj a'q. weig zu'g meib Bua tu'q liud sivj livb, sivj livb zyrug Faauj Euvb Euvg meib Bua. ninb Eei waag yaag zyen Eei, maiq Jaaq. sivj livb Faauj meib Bua Navq haiq nx Zauj ki-tug Jwavg mcvg zyavb, meib Bua zyrug xij zu'g Navq uaq nx zruj.
2.11: haiq taub maiq Namq ninb Eei kxb yrud, uaq taub yem Mwavj ka'Euad. ninb se Navq yavb Mwavj Eei txvj nx, maiq hiuq tu'q ninb mivb haaij, weig zu'g Mwavj pun ninb Eei mziv Navq mcvb nx.
2.5: haiq taub ei Jyenq Tinb huvb Eei waag zruj, uaq taub za'kevb Namq Tinb huvb Tauj taaub a'q. Navq naaig, Bua zyrug hiuq tu'q Bua Zauj Tinb huvb Jwavg mcvg zyavb.
2.9: haiq taub kxvq ninb yem Fav mq paag Rxv ninb Eei kxb yrud, uaq taub Zxg yem Mwavj ka'Euad.
2.16: weig zu'g yetg zuvq yem paamb ken Eei ka'naaiq se paamb myenb hang Eei, mziv pwatg zyrug mweig Jia'q Eei, Zauj myenb Zevb Lo, zruj mauj Eei sig. naaiq teij yetg zuvq se yem paamb ken Zwrtq taaib Eei, maiq zeid yem zavg tiaj taaib.
2.4: haiq taub kxvq ninb hiuq tu'q Tinb huvb yaag maiq ei Jyenq Tinb huvb Eei livg zruj, uaq taub Kuvj kxvb pc'g Navq. zyen leid maiq yem ninb Eei Hruq a'q.
2.10: haiq taub Namq ninb Eei kxb yrud zyrug yem Fav ka'Euad. ninb yaag maiq maaib haiq Euvg Duaq haiq taub paamd zwid.
2.22: uaq Euvg, haiq taub kxvb pc'g? se tovb maiq Eyemg ye-su zruj ki-tug uaq taub. uaq taub zruj ki-tug Eei winb wavq, laaij ninb maiq Eyemg zavg tiaj yaag maiq Eyemg zavg tiaj Eei txn.
2.12: fu'Jweiq aa'b! yia fiaq fyenj pun meib Bua weig zu'g meib Bua weig ki-tug tu'q kwavg liud meib Bua Eei zwid.
2.15: maiq tuvq Namq paamb ken fai Namq paamb ken Eei ka'naaiq. haiq taub Namq paamb ken, uaq taub maiq maaib Hruq Namq zavg tiaj.
2.13: zruj tia Eei zwavj myenb aa'b! yia fiaq fyenj pun meib Bua weig zu'g meib Bua hiuq tu'q maiq kcvb zeij luvb zeij Dau yem Eei uaq taub. meib Bua myenb lunj myenb aa'b! yia fiaq fyenj pun meib Bua weig zu'g meib Bua hivb Jiaj Ywav x'q uaq taub mig a'q. fu'Jweiq aa'b! yia fiaq fyenj pun meib Bua weig zu'g meib Bua hiuq tu'q zavg tiaj.
2.1: yia Eei fu'Jweiq aa'b! yia Navq naaiq nx fiaq pun meib Bua weig pun meib Bua maiq paamd zwid. sij kxvq haiq taub paamd zwid nx, Bua maaib taub Tevj Bua Toq zavg tiaj, se pcvb fim Eei uaq taub, ye-su ki-tug.
2.26: yia fiaq naaiq teij waag pun meib Bua hiuq tu'q Duaq meib Bua uaq teij myenb.
2.25: naaiq se ki-tug kanb lcvd Eei vcvg waag. ninb lcvd pun Bua tu'q yetg liud Eei mcvg.
